com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.pipeline.VisitResult

  • Packages that use VisitResult 
    Package Description
    com.noctarius.borabora.spi.query.pipeline
    This package contains all interfaces required to either implement custom QueryStages or complete QueryPipeline implementations together with their according factories and the pipeline flow control VisitResult.
